ch APIs to rapidly move from initial design ideas to polished shipping applications. Topics range from getting started to advanced update animations and layouts.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc18-225-a-tour-of-uicollectionview","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC18-225-A-Tour-of-UICollectionView","type":"topic"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC17":{"url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc17","title":"WWDC17","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Xcode 9, Swift 4.0, iOS 11, macOS 10.13 (High Sierra), tvOS 11, watchOS 4."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"New APIs: "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Core NFC"},{"type":"text","text":" and more."}],"kind":"article","images":[{"identifier":"WWDC17-Icon.png","type":"icon"},{"identifier":"WWDC17.jpeg","type":"card"}],"role":"collectionGroup"},"WWDC17-Icon.png":{"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17-Icon.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"alt":null,"type":"image","identifier":"WWDC17-Icon.png"},"WWDC17.jpeg":{"variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17.jpeg"}],"type":"image","identifier":"WWDC17.jpeg","alt":null},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC21-10059-Whats-new-in-UIKit":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC21-10059-Whats-new-in-UIKit","role":"sampleCode","kind":"article","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Discover the latest updates and improvements to UIKit and learn how to build better iPadOS, iOS, and Mac Catalyst apps. We’ll take you through UI refinements, productivity updates, and API enhancements, and help you explore performance improvements and security & privacy features."}],"title":"What’s new in UIKit","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc21-10059-whats-new-in-uikit"},"https://wwdcnotes.com/documentation/wwdcnotes/contributing":{"type":"link","title":"Learn More…",